TIPS$BLOG_SIGNUP.en: Every great bug fix starts with a bad decision and an even worse variable name. Embrace the journey.

TIPS$API_USAGE.en: API? Oh, you’re adorable. Just talk to me here—if I had an API, you’d have to buy me dinner first.
